---
---
<section class="page-container section-spacer">
  <div class="section-rule"></div>
  <p class="eyebrow fade-in">engineering</p>
  <h2 class="fade-in-up delay-1" style="max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);">Verified in CI, not marketing.</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);">
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-2">
      <h4 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent);">Technical</h4>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">128 automated tests (92 backend + 36 frontend)</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">Field-level Fernet encryption at rest</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">OS keyring auth with file fallback</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">Rate limiting via slowapi</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">CSP, X-Frame-Options: DENY, nosniff headers</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">Multi-arch Docker (amd64 + arm64)</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">Loopback-only binding (127.0.0.1)</div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">Full threat model in SECURITY.md</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-3">
      <h4 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent);">Architecture</h4>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink);">One domain layer</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">, MCP, REST, Telegram bot all call the same functions.</span>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink);">SQLite on disk</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">. Never in repo, never iCloud. Your machine, your database.</span>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink);">PWA installable</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">. Safari Add to Dock, Android Install App. Offline-capable.</span>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink);">AGPL-3.0</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary);">. Free to self-host and modify. Public service must offer source.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
